news.title: Credai-Nashik to initiate vaccination drive for construction workers
news.para: Credia Nashik unit president Ravi Mahajan said registration for the vaccination drive has started and on-site vaccination would be conducted with the help of a private hospital.

news.title: RWAs urge Noida authority to penalise owners of vacant plots
news.para: The Noida Authority, Sharma added, must impose an appropriate fine on all such plots or houses owners or investors, who mostly are waiting to sell them for a profit rather than use for residential purposes.

news.title: Avail estate office services in Chandigarh at a click
news.para: With this, multiple services of the estate office, like property registration, transfer, sale, mutation, no objection certificates (NOC), and revised building plan approval, can be availed at a click. Besides, the required documents can be uploaded and payments made online.
